  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is buffet style with options like pastries, yoghurt, fruit salad, toast, tea, coffee and fruit juices all served in the Italian Taste restaurant. If you're staying on half board dinner will be a choice of four courses, including a salad and dessert buffet.</p>
<p><strong>Italian Taste</strong> is the hotel's main restaurant and serves authentic Italian food for breakfast and dinner. Open for breakfast from 7am - 10.30am and dinner 7pm - 9.30pm. </p>
<p><strong>Sparkling Lounge Bar </strong>is the hotel's comfortable bar area where you can taste original cocktails. There's a small kitchen serving light food and snacks (payable locally).</p>
<p>Early meals for children are available on request.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
