  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Aqualux Suites &amp; Terme is the ideal hotel for a relaxing break. This luxurious hotel gives you a real sense of getting away from it all. Best of all, the bustling centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1}" title="Bardolino">Bardolino</a> is just a 20-minute walk away so there’s plenty to explore.</p>
<h2>State-of-the-art spa</h2>
<p>The Aqualux Hotel is the ideal place for a relaxing break. Its state-of-the-art spa is the star of the show. At over 1,000 square metres, there are several saunas, a relaxation area and various treatments on the menu. It has four indoor pools including; one for children, a hydro-massage pool with waterfalls, an elevated pool surrounded by comfy sofas, and one that connects to the outdoor pool.</p>
<h2>Sustainable values</h2>
<p>The wellness theme is carried on throughout the hotel. Two restaurants focus on Italian cuisine and organic produce. There are some fantastic dishes on the menu and we recommend trying as many as you can. The hotel was built using ecological materials and is environmentally friendly (a certified CLIMA hotel).</p>]]></description>
