  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Rooms</strong> are around 28m² and sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed). Please request twin or double beds at the time of booking.</p>
<p><strong>Aqua Rooms</strong> are around 30-32m<span>² and can sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed). They overlook the garden and pools. Please request twin or double beds at the time of booking.</span></p>
<p><strong>Garden Suites</strong> are around 50m<span>² and sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed). They have a separate bedroom and living area. These suites are available on request, please call to book.</span></p>
<p><strong>Comfort Rooms for sole use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p><span>A resort tax of approx. €1.50 per person per night is payable locally.</span></p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
